comments: Towns (MIN) establishes himself in a screening position in the path of Conley (UTA) and absorbs the incoming contact.
Towns (MIN) slightly extends his arm into Conley's (UTA) body and does not dislodge him from his legally obtained position.
Niang (UTA) maintains a legal guarding position during the driving shot attempt by Edwards (MIN) as he keeps his arm vertical and absorbs the contact.
McDaniels (MIN) places his hand to Ingles' (UTA) front at the start of his drive and affects his SQBR.  The inadvertent contact to McDaniels' head occurs after the illegal contact.
Towns (MIN) briefly grasps Ingles' (UTA) arm during the pick and does not affect his ability to defend.
Towns (MIN) moves laterally along Conley's (UTA) path during his drive and the contact is marginal.
Gobert (UTA) extends his arm into Russell's (MIN) body and dislodges him from his legally obtained position during the screen.
Towns (MIN) establishes himself in a screening position in the path of Ingles (UTA), firms up, and absorbs the incoming contact during the pick.
Towns (MIN) slightly extends his arm into Gobert's (UTA) body and does not dislodge him from his legally obtained position during the rebound.
Gobert (UTA) places his hand on McDaniels (MIN) as he runs along the baseline in attempt to make the inbounds pass.
Ingles (UTA) cleanly deflects the incoming pass to Russell (MIN) in the backcourt.
Gobert (UTA) cleanly deflects the ball away from Towns (MIN) and avoids making contact to his arm.
McDaniels (MIN) commits a take foul on Conley (UTA).
Towns (MIN) wraps his arm around Gobert's (UTA) body and affects his FOM during the rebound.
Ingles (UTA) establishes a screening position in Rubio's (MIN) path inbounds as he absorbs the incoming contact.
Rubio (MIN) makes incidental contact to Conley's (UTA) arm after the release of his jump shot attempt.
Russell (MIN) takes fewer than three steps after he has gathered the ball.
Rubio (MIN) cleanly deflects the ball from Conley (UTA) during his dribble.
Conley (UTA) swipes down and makes slight contact with McDaniels' (MIN) arm and does not affect his ability to gather the loose ball.
